98715.name: Our World in Data Visitors (past year)
98715.description:
Number of users to ourworldindata.org in the period from October 2017-2018. This is given by past year, past month and past week.

Past year data runs from 7th October 2017 - 7th October 2018.

Past month from 7th September 2018 - 7th October 2018.

Past week from 30th September 2018 - 7th October 2018.
